%% Diagram: Linear-style sync engine — local mutation queue, lastSyncId, delta packets
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as UI
    participant POOL as Object pool (MobX)
    participant TXQ as Tx queue + IndexedDB
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant SYNC as Sync service
    participant DB as Postgres

    Note over UI,POOL: Local write
    UI->>POOL: issue.title = "..."
    POOL->>TXQ: enqueue Tx{op,entity,fields,baseSyncId}
    TXQ-->>UI: ack (UI re-renders instantly)

    TXQ->>WS: send Tx (online)
    WS->>SYNC: Tx
    SYNC->>DB: persist + bump lastSyncId
    DB-->>SYNC: lastSyncId = N
    SYNC-->>WS: ack(Tx, syncId=N)
    WS-->>TXQ: ack — drop from queue

    Note over SYNC,WS: Fan-out to other clients
    SYNC->>WS: delta packet {syncActions, lastSyncId=N}
    WS-->>POOL: apply delta
    POOL-->>UI: re-render

    Note over TXQ,WS: Reconnect after offline
    TXQ->>WS: GET /sync/delta from=baseSyncId to=current
    WS-->>TXQ: missed deltas
    TXQ->>TXQ: rebase queued Tx onto new base
    TXQ->>WS: replay remaining Tx
